        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=54101&amp;TOPIC_ID=6624&amp;FORUM_ID=2&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=General+Discussions&amp;Topic_Title=DC+pets+in+a+group+of+2%2B&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Vindicator raid on old server...</P><P>Group had two enchanters (both epic-ed), one rogue (epic), one paladin, one magician (epic), and one druid. </P><P>Both enchanters had dire charmed giant guards. I didn't really notice any loss in exp and we ended up KS-ing every group there, even got final kill on Vindicator.</P><P>Rogue and Paladin probably did enough damage to out weigh the damage done by the two dire charmed giants though.</P><P>Kalyi<BR>Necromancer of Luclin<BR>"Look around you... I am death."<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
